Phase 1 — Test Harness

- [ ] Add request-capture utility for service tests (`URLProtocol` or APIClient test double).
- [ ] Add shared assertion helpers for method/path/query/header/body checks.
- [ ] Add JSON fixture loader for test payloads.
- [ ] Add backend mode selector utility (`SWIFT_REST_BACKEND=mocked|real`, default mocked).
- [ ] Add reusable XCTest skip guard for tests requiring real backend.

Phase 2 — MbooksService Contract Tests

- [ ] Create `MbooksServiceTests.swift`.
- [ ] Add tests for `moviesPaging(query:)` and `moviesSearch(query:)`.
