- [ ] Add tests for `adminAddScreen(body:)`, `adminUpdateScreen(body:)`, `adminDeleteScreen(body:)`.
- [ ] Assert method/path/query/body/header contract for each endpoint.
- [ ] Add mock fixture mappings for all listed mbooks endpoints.

Phase 3 — LoginGatewayService Contract Tests

- [ ] Create `LoginGatewayServiceTests.swift`.
